Package: serverhub-agent
Version: VERSION_PLACEHOLDER
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: N30Z <admin@serverhub.local>
Depends: systemd
Description: ServerHub Agent — Linux server monitoring & management
 Self-contained Linux agent that collects system metrics (CPU, memory,
 disk, network, processes, services, Docker containers) and serves the
 ServerHub web dashboard + REST/WebSocket API on port 8080.
 .
 Install and visit http://<server-ip>:8080 to access the dashboard.
